{"type":"data","nodes":[null,{"type":"data","data":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Analyse du Handbook de GitLab","created_at":"2019-02-14"},"body":"<html><head></head><body><h1 id=\"analyse-du-handbook-de-gitlab\" tabindex=\"-1\"></h1>\n<nav class=\"table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#que-contient-le-handbook-de-gitlab\">Que contient le handbook de GitLab ? </a></li><li><a href=\"#qui-utilise-et-qui-contribue-au-handbook\">Qui utilise et qui contribue au Handbook ? </a></li></ul></nav><h2 id=\"que-contient-le-handbook-de-gitlab\" tabindex=\"-1\">Que contient le handbook de GitLab ? <a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#que-contient-le-handbook-de-gitlab\">\n                    <span aria-hidden=\"true\">¶</span>\n                </a></h2>\n<p>Liste des types d’informations présents dans le Handbook de GitLab (cette liste ne paraphrase pas <a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/\">son sommaire</a>) :</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/values/\">Les valeurs, l’état d’esprit des employés de GitLab</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/leadership/\">Règles de management et de leadership</a></li>\n<li>Outils, procédures et bonnes pratiques, concernant :\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/security/\">la sécurité informatique</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/communication/\">la communication au sein de GitLab</a> (comment et quand utiliser l’email, le chat, les viséoconférences…)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/hiring/\">le recrutement</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/general-onboarding/\">l’onboarding</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/spending-company-money/\">notes de frais, dépenses d’argent</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Règle de fonctionnement, ressources… de chaque équipe (<a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/#engineering-departments--teams\">liste des équipes du département Engineering</a>)</li>\n<li>La description précise de tous les jobs (role) (examples : <a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/blob/master/source/job-families/engineering/backend-engineer/index.html.md#staff-backend-engineer\">\nStaff Backend Engineer</a>, <a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/blob/master/source/job-families/engineering/backend-engineer/index.html.md#engineering-manager\">\nEngineering Manager</a>, <a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/blob/master/source/job-families/engineering/chief-technology-officer/index.html.md\">CTO</a>, <a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/blob/master/source/job-families/engineering/database-engineer/index.html.md\">database engineer</a>…), chaque job contient les informations suivantes :\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/blob/master/source/job-families/engineering/database-engineer/index.html.md#responsibilities\">Responsibilities</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/blob/master/source/job-families/engineering/database-engineer/index.html.md#example-projects\">Example Projects</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/blob/master/source/job-families/engineering/database-engineer/index.html.md#requirements\">Requirements</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/blob/master/source/job-families/engineering/database-engineer/index.html.md#nice-to-haves\">Nice-to-have’s</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/blob/master/source/job-families/engineering/database-engineer/index.html.md#hiring-process\">Hiring Process</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/company/team/org-chart/\">L’organisation des équipes, de la hiérarchie complète et précise</a>, il est possible de cliquer sur chaque poste pour comprendre avec précision le périmètre de chacun</li>\n<li>Exemple de sujets abordés dans les pages “équipes” :\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/dev-backend/distribution/#mission\">Mission</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/dev-backend/distribution/#vision\">Vision</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/dev-backend/distribution/#technology\">Technology</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/dev-backend/distribution/#team\">Team</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/dev-backend/distribution/#team-members\">Team members</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/dev-backend/distribution/#stable-counterparts\">Stable counterparts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/dev-backend/distribution/#team-responsibility\">Team responsibility</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/dev-backend/distribution/#team-objectives\">Team objectives</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/dev-backend/distribution/#projects\">Projects</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/dev-backend/distribution/#projects\">Onboarding and offboarding</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/dev-backend/distribution/#work-resources\">Work Resources</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/dev-backend/distribution/#infrastructure-and-maintenance\">Infrastructure and maintenance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/engineering/dev-backend/distribution/#team-workflows\">Team workflows</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"qui-utilise-et-qui-contribue-au-handbook\" tabindex=\"-1\">Qui utilise et qui contribue au Handbook ? <a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#qui-utilise-et-qui-contribue-au-handbook\">\n                    <span aria-hidden=\"true\">¶</span>\n                </a></h2>\n<p>Chez GitLab, tous les employés utilisent et contribuent au Handbook :</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/leadership/#c-group\">C-group</a> (CEO, CFO, …), <a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/leadership/#e-group\">E-group</a>, <a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/leadership/#s-group\">S-group</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/commits/master/source/handbook/people-operations/index.html.md\">Les RH</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/commits/master/source/handbook/engineering/index.html.md\">Les ingénieurs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/gitlab-com/www-gitlab-com/commits/master/source/handbook/marketing/index.html.md\">Les personnes du marketing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/sales/\">Les Sales</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/finance/\">Finance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/product/\">Product</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://about.gitlab.com/handbook/legal/\">Juridique</a></li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>"},"uses":{"params":["page_slug"]}}]}